divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking three images of a mountain top in order to photo stitch themtogether for a panorama picture. When I down loaded them I saw the object in thesecond or middle image. I saw nothing unusual in my field of vision as I snappedthe picture. I have saved the original image in my memory card. It is the sameas the day I took the picture. I cannot describe the action or movement of theobject because, as I stated, I didnt see it until the image was down loaded andenlarged in my software program. Please let me know if I can be of futher help.
